                                <p>The woman’s right arm is bent across the front of the body; the
                                    left arm is raised, grasping the edge of her veil. She wears a
                                    diadem with a palm motif at the forehead, along with two
                                    necklaces. Her features include a high forehead, flattened nasal
                                    bridge, small mouth with a full lower lip, and a strong
                                    jawline.</p>
